{
  "info": {
    "name": "GearUp API",
    "description": "# GearUp API — Complete Test Collection\n\n## 📋 About\nFull API collection for **GearUp** — a sports & outdoor gear rental platform.\n\n---\n\n## 🔐 Authentication Flow\n1. **Register** a CUSTOMER and PROVIDER (or use seeded users)\n2. **Login** → JWT token auto-saved to `{{customerToken}}` / `{{providerToken}}` / `{{adminToken}}`\n3. Protected endpoints automatically use the saved tokens\n\n---\n\n## 🏗️ Complete Rental Flow (execute in order)\n\n```\nStep 1  →  Register/Login Customer & Provider\nStep 2  →  [Provider] Create Category\nStep 3  →  [Provider] Create Gear  (POST /api/provider/gear)\nStep 4  →  [Customer] Browse Gear  (GET /api/gear)\nStep 5  →  [Customer] Create Rental Order  (POST /api/rentals)  →  PLACED\nStep 6  →  [Provider] Confirm Order  (PATCH /api/provider/orders/:id)  →  CONFIRMED\nStep 7  →  [Customer] Create Checkout Session  (POST /api/payments/create)\nStep 8  →  Open checkout URL in browser, pay with card 4242...\nStep 9  →  [Customer] Confirm Payment  (POST /api/payments/confirm)  →  PAID\nStep 10 →  [Provider] Mark Picked Up  →  PICKED_UP\nStep 11 →  [Provider] Mark Returned  →  RETURNED\nStep 12 →  [Customer] Leave Review  (POST /api/reviews)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💳 Test Card for Stripe\n| Card Number | Expiry | CVC |\n|-------------|--------|-----|\n| `4242 4242 4242 4242` | Any future date | Any 3 digits |\n\n---\n\n## 🧪 Seeded Test Accounts\nRun `npm run seed` to create these users:\n| Role | Email | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| ADMIN | `admin@gearup.com` | `admin123` |\n| PROVIDER | `provider@gearup.com` | `provider123` |\n| CUSTOMER | `customer@gearup.com` | `customer123` |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "GearUp-Backend"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "providerToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "adminToken", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "gearId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "categoryId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "rentalOrderId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "transactionId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customerId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "providerId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "paymentId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "reviewId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🛡️ Authentication",
